        ProjectResultReport postRepositoryProject(RepositoryProjectExecutionRequest executionRequest,
                                          boolean async,
                                          HttpBasicAuth auth)
                                   throws ApiException
        Executes a project from an existing repository on TestServer
        Parameters:
        executionRequest - request with execution details
        async - true if request should be executed asynchronously
        auth - credentials container
        Returns:
        ProjectResultReport with current state of the execution.
        Throws:
        ApiException - if validation fails or server returns with an error

      • postSwagger

        ProjectResultReport postSwagger(File swaggerFile,
                                SwaggerApiValidator.SwaggerFormat swaggerFormat,
                                String endpoint,
                                String callBackUrl,
                                boolean async,
                                HttpBasicAuth auth)
                         throws ApiException
        Submit Swagger specification file to TestServer to create and execute tests for each api defined in specifications.
        Parameters:
        swaggerFile - Swagger file
        swaggerFormat - format
        endpoint - endpoint against which tests should be executed. Tests will be executed against the host specified in Swagger definition if endpoint is not provided.
        async - true if request should be executed asynchronously
        auth - credentials container
        Returns:
        execution
        Throws:
        ApiException
